attributes.Long form description: The instructor tells the student to start assembling the stool. He then inspects the pieces of the chair and takes the legs to see how to put them on. The instructor tells him how to start the assembly correctly. The student grabs the legs of the stool and places them correctly following the instructions of the instructor. Afterwards, the student takes the hex nut and the bolt and turns the legs over the table and begins to screw them by hand, and then with a wrench. The student turns the legs of the stool and grabs the seat to place it on top, but the instructor tells him how to place it. Then, inserting the legs over the seat, the student begins to bolt them to the seat. The man takes the first screw and saddler washer and after placing them in his hand, he places them on the first leg screwing them to it with a screwdriver. Then, he continues screwing into the leg with the second screw and the saddle washer also with the screwdriver. The student screws the third and fourth screws together with the saddler washers with the screwdriver. Finally, the man turns the assembled chair over the table.

attributes.Transcription: We will now assemble a stool from IKEA.
So please go ahead and assemble it.
